RAI Research Corp said it appearsthat the reduced level of sales may continue for the near term.    Earlier, RAI reported that third quarter net declined to17,806 dlrs on sales of 1.3 mln dlrs from net income of 328,290dlrs on sales of 2.2 mln dlrs a year ago.   It said sales declined as a result of reduced sales ofpermion battery separators to Japanese customers and it doesnot know the duration or extent of these factors. Reuter&#3;